Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.27,0:05:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14\pos(611,05)}SAMURAI DO PAÍS DE WA\NKIN'EMON, RAPOSA DE FOGO
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.27,0:05:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs16\pos(900,05)}EX-PRINCESA DE DRESSROSA\NVIOLA
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.27,0:05:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14\pos(1135,128)}PIRATA DOS CHAPÉUS DE PALHA\NFRANKY, O CIBORGUE
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.27,0:05:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs25\clip(0,0,1280,720)\be0.6\fscx89.96\fscy89.96\bord2\pos(151,175)}PIRATA DOS\N CHAPÉUS DE PALHA\NZORO, O CAÇADOR DE PIRATAS
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.27,0:05:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs25\clip(0,0,1280,720)\be0.6\fscx89.98\fscy89.98\bord2\pos(565,175)}EX-CAPITÃO DO \NEXÉRCITO DE DRESSROSA\NKYROS
